 					http://www.history.com/news/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/measuring.jpg
                    
					To identify the age and gender of various flutings’ creators, archaeologists devised a technique based on hand measurements. (Credit: Jessica Cooney/Leslie Van Gelder)
