					Close View of a Fluting
                    
 					http://www.history.com/news/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/fluting-width.jpg
                    
					They concluded that flutings with a width of 1.3 inches or less were made by children age 7 or under. (Credit: Jessica Cooney/Leslie Van Gelder)
