					Set of Flutings on a Cave Wall
                    
 					http://www.history.com/news/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/flutings-set.jpg
                    
					The method allowed them to determine that children as young as 2 were responsible for many of the flutings at Rouffignac, and nearly all in one particular chamber. (Credit: Jessica Cooney/Leslie Van Gelder)
