					Markings Located High on the Ceiling
                    
 					http://www.history.com/news/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/high-fluting.jpg
                    
					Because children would not have been able to reach the surfaces on which some flutings were etched, it is believed that adults lifted and helped them. (Credit: Jessica Cooney/Leslie Van Gelder)
